    # game/areas/prologue.rpy:1433
    old "“Here’s the catch.” She dusts off the hilt of her sword. “We’ve hired a messenger to ask the commanders for further orders. Since she hasn’t returned and you know nothing about her, she either ran away or something happened to her,” she sighs with resignation. “We are meant to stay here until fall. What do you think? Come see us, tell us what you’ve learned about the man, and we’ll get back to {color=#f6d6bd}Hovlavan{/color} together?” \n\nYou think about your {i}real{/i} mission. You were planning to return to {color=#f6d6bd}Hovlavan{/color} in the early fall anyway. "
