    new ""

    # game/areas/prologue.rpy:1930
    old "Both soldiers are standing near a humble pyre. {color=#f6d6bd}The man in the shirt{/color} looks at it contemplatively. {color=#f6d6bd}Tulia{/color} is the first one to address you. \n\n“[pcname],” she greets you with a nod. “We used the horse’s manure for the flames, so don’t worry about cleaning it up.” \n\nYou see a corpse among the flames. It’s impossible to tell if it belongs to a male or a female, but it was an adult. \n\nThe burning process won’t be over for a couple more hours. "
